<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <% include ../partials/head %> 
  <title>
    Welcome to Lose It
  </title>
</head>

<body class="landing-page sidebar-collapse">
    <% include ../partials/navbar %> 
  <div class="page-header header-filter" data-parallax="true" style="background-color: lightskyblue; height: 500px;">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-10 col-lg-8 col-xl-7 mx-auto">

                <% if (errors.length) { %>
         
                    <div class = 'alert alert-danger alert-dismissable'>
                    <button type='button' class='close' data-dismiss='alert' aria-label='Close'>
                      <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                    </button>
                    <%= errors %>
                    </div>
                     <% } %>

                     <% if (success.length) { %>
         
                        <div class = 'alert alert-success alert-dismissable'>
                        <button type='button' class='close' data-dismiss='alert' aria-label='Close'>
                          <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                        </button>
                        <%= success %>
                        </div>
                         <% } %>
                   
              <% if (!user) { %>
                <div class="col-xl-9 mx-auto">
                    <h1 class="mb-5">Get Started today to achieve your goal</h1>
                  </div>
                <form role="form" method="POST" action="/api/v1/users/register">
                    <div class="form-row">
                      <div class="col-12 col-md-9 mb-2 mb-md-0">
                        <input type="email" name="email" id="email"class="form-control form-control-lg" placeholder="Enter your email..." style="color: white;">
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-12 col-md-3">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-block btn-lg btn-primary">Sign up!</button>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </form>
              <% } %>

              <% if (user) { %>
                <div class="col-xl-9 mx-auto">
                    <h1 class="mb-5">Welcome Back <%= user.name %> </h1>
                  </div>
              <% } %>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="main main-raised">
    <div class="container">

        <% if (user) { %>

            
            <% if (!user.userInfo.userInfo) { %>
                <div class="section text-center">
                    <div class="row">
                      <div class="col-md-8 ml-auto mr-auto">
                        <h2 class="title">Before we get Started , Please Complete your  <a href="/ap1/v1/users/account/userinfo" style="text-decoration: underline; color: skyblue;">info </a> </h2>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
            <% } %>
            <% } %>
                  <% if (!user) { %>
                    <div class="section text-center">
                        <div class="row">
                          <div class="col-md-8 ml-auto mr-auto">
                            <h2 class="title">Let&apos;s talk product</h2>
                            <h5 class="description">This is the paragraph where you can write more details about your product. Keep you user engaged by providing meaningful information. Remember that by this time, the user is curious, otherwise he wouldn&apos;t scroll to get here. Add a button if you want the user to see more.</h5>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="features">
                          <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                              <div class="info">
                                <div class="icon icon-info">
                                  <i class="material-icons">chat</i>
                                </div>
                                <h4 class="info-title">Free Chat</h4>
                                <p>Divide details about your product or agency work into parts. Write a few lines about each one. A paragraph describing a feature will be enough.</p>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                              <div class="info">
                                <div class="icon icon-success">
                                  <i class="material-icons">verified_user</i>
                                </div>
                                <h4 class="info-title">Verified Users</h4>
                                <p>Divide details about your product or agency work into parts. Write a few lines about each one. A paragraph describing a feature will be enough.</p>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                              <div class="info">
                                <div class="icon icon-danger">
                                  <i class="material-icons">fingerprint</i>
                                </div>
                                <h4 class="info-title">Fingerprint</h4>
                                <p>Divide details about your product or agency work into parts. Write a few lines about each one. A paragraph describing a feature will be enough.</p>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                  <% } %>
           
    </div>
  </div>

  <% include ../partials/footer %> 
  <% include ../partials/script %> 
  
</body>

</html>